entry.title: Blasts Hit Crimean Port Where Russian Fleet Is Based
entry.content: Russian-installed officials in the occupied Ukrainian peninsula said air defenses had shot down several drones in the early hours of the morning, including an unmanned surface drone in the waters off Sevastopol.

entry.title: Afghan Evacuees in Limbo While Seeking Permanent Legal Status in the U.S.
entry.content: Bipartisan legislation to grant legal status to people who fled last year’s Taliban takeover is stalled over Republicans’ security concerns.
